# 21.dev redirects
# Path-based redirects for the main site
#
# Syntax: source destination [status]
# Example: /old-path /new-path 301
#
# Status codes: 301 (permanent), 302 (temporary)
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Note: Canonical domain redirect (www.21.dev â†’ 21.dev) remains in
# Cloudflare Rules due to requiring dynamic expressions.

